description:
Competitive Offer Process: September 5th – September 11th. Interested buyers should submit offers by September 4th for early consideration. Contact listing agent for full participation details.
Welcome to the Printer's Alley Penthouse. Rich in Nashville history & vibrant culture, this exclusive downtown loft is where industrial charm & Nashville character meets modern luxury. Located atop the iconic Phoenix Lofts, this 3,183-square-foot, fully furnished penthouse offers a one-of-a-kind opportunity for the discerning buyer. Featuring 4 bedrooms & 4.5 bathrooms, the open-concept design is bathed in natural light from floor-to-ceiling windows, highlighting the exposed brick walls, wood-beamed ceilings, & industrial details. Thoughtfully curated furnishings & decor, blending timeless elegance with artistic flair, are included, making this home truly move-in ready. Entertain effortlessly in the expansive living area, complete with billiards table and bold Music City design elements that pay homage to Nashville’s roots in music & culture. Enjoy 12 foot ceilings through the living space. The gourmet kitchen features high-end appliances, rich cabinetry, & a layout perfect for hosting intimate dinners or larger gatherings.
The 600-square-foot private rooftop terrace is a show-stopper, offering sweeping skyline views, wet bar, gas fire pit, & comfortable seating to soak in Music City. Whether enjoying a quiet morning or an evening with friends, this outdoor retreat defines Nashville luxury. Sitting in the heart of historic Printer’s Alley, you’re steps away from Broadway’s live music, award-winning restaurants like Skull's Rainbow Room, & boutique shopping, yet high above it all in your private urban sanctuary. If you’re looking for a turnkey home that combines exclusivity, style, & the best of Music City, the Printer’s Alley Penthouse is your match. Schedule your private showing today & experience this one-of-a-kind property for yourself.
